script: var ratio = 0; function startFunc () { var list = document.getElementsByTagName("div"); ratio = list[0].offsetWidth / list[0].offsetHeight; console.log(list[0].offsetWidth); console.log(list[0].offsetHeight); console.log("Ratio 1 = "+ratio); } window.addEventListener("load", function(event) { startFunc(); fit(); }); fit(); window.addEventListener("resize", fit , true ); function fit() { startFunc(); let cont_height = window.innerHeight; let cont_width = window.innerWidth; console.log("Ratio = "+ratio); if ( window.innerHeight*ratio > window.innerWidth ) { console.log("width - is bottleneck"); cont_width = window.innerWidth; cont_height = cont_width/ratio; }else{ console.log("height - is bottleneck"); cont_height = window.innerHeight; cont_width = cont_height*ratio; } var cont = document.getElementsByTagName("div")[0]; cont.style.height = cont_height + "px"; cont.style.width = cont_width + "px"; }
